dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data is intended to be used to assign regions to the to the secchi depth records.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data is comprised of polygons that represent the subregions of the Rose/Smith Delta Smelt bioenergetics model. The polygons were digitized on 11/12/2020 using Fig. 2.3.2 from "Structured Decision Making for Scientific Management in the San Francisco Bay-Delta" as the reference.
